divs: Sighting DetailsI was at Thunder Falls in Mackinaw city I took pictures of the park, when I got home Inoticed orbs in the pictures. It seems as though orbs are travelling through the beams coming from above. It almost looks like a spider web and upon closer examination I realized these beams were coming from the sky and were going behind people. Please look closley. I also took a picture of the mackinaw island from the bridge and when I got home I noticed a craft in picture. I have no idea what kind of craft it is.
Summary: I was taking pictures at Thunder Falls and noticed orbs in the pics after. It looks like there are orbs travelling down the beams of light. I also took a photo of Mackinaw Island from the bridge and noticed a craft in it when I got home.
